== Installation

[source]
----
pip3 install -r requirements.txt
----

python3 was not linked, so had to:

[source]
----
brew link --overwrite python
----

== Tests
To run the tests, run:

[source]
----
./run-tests.sh
----

Tun run a single test, from root run:

[source]
----
./run-tests.sh <name of test>
----

== Packaging

[source]
----
pip3 wheel -r requirements.txt
----
